723144f-a.title: Manhattan: St. Nicholas Avenue - 158th Street
723144f-a.text:
953-55-57 St. Nicholas Avenue (old Kingsbridge Road) at S.W. corner
of 158th Street. These three wooden houses were built around 1895.
October 12, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
